  "detailed_description": "<strong>The most funny Sim game this year !!!</strong><br>What will you play if you have a very drunk friend？A warm hearted angel?Or an evil<br>bad guy？You may find answer in this fun sim game. Try exploring in the room and <br>figure out how to sober up your friend,may it's not only just one solution,though,never<br>hurt your friend,and never do evil!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966530/extras/09b14e9fba356a75e7214769e05a6e48.avif?t=1680275574\" width=600 height=296 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966530/extras/038147806fab441645f73a3ea93901e0.avif?t=1680275574\" width=600 height=256 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fun Dynamic Puppet Tech.,characters behave different when target/envirment changes</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Total random drunk behaviour,you never know what will friend act when you try a move</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Amazing physics simulation，high end softbody and fluid sim.The wind blow ground to dry，water will wet your body..</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can interact with almost every item,physics sim +puzzle solving</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>We will update more contents regularly</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fun,real fun!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966530/extras/cdbd482413dec169aa3e2599b72cc956.poster.avif?t=1680275574\" width=626 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966530/extras/cdbd482413dec169aa3e2599b72cc956.webm?t=1680275574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966530/extras/cdbd482413dec169aa3e2599b72cc956.mp4?t=1680275574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966530/extras/374d411a070e2ce7ff81a4261640b99b.poster.avif?t=1680275574\" width=626 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966530/extras/374d411a070e2ce7ff81a4261640b99b.webm?t=1680275574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966530/extras/374d411a070e2ce7ff81a4261640b99b.mp4?t=1680275574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>The most funny Sim game this year !!!</strong><br>What will you play if you have a very drunk friend？A warm hearted angel?Or an evil<br>bad guy？You may find answer in this fun sim game. Try exploring in the room and <br>figure out how to sober up your friend,may it's not only just one solution,though,never<br>hurt your friend,and never do evil!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966530/extras/09b14e9fba356a75e7214769e05a6e48.avif?t=1680275574\" width=600 height=296 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966530/extras/038147806fab441645f73a3ea93901e0.avif?t=1680275574\" width=600 height=256 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fun Dynamic Puppet Tech.,characters behave different when target/envirment changes</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Total random drunk behaviour,you never know what will friend act when you try a move</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Amazing physics simulation，high end softbody and fluid sim.The wind blow ground to dry，water will wet your body..</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can interact with almost every item,physics sim +puzzle solving</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>We will update more contents regularly</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fun,real fun!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966530/extras/cdbd482413dec169aa3e2599b72cc956.poster.avif?t=1680275574\" width=626 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966530/extras/cdbd482413dec169aa3e2599b72cc956.webm?t=1680275574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/